{"tid":22864,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[MVC framwork] 新中高手都傾下","createTime":"2016-12-04T15:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T01:43:37.000Z","uid":49145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64884b8ea660cd1d35a988ac6678a3069941edb1","tid":22864,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"小弟自己興趣寫下網頁 之前返工就用codeingiter既 近期又想寫個新既 就諗緊用angularjs定node.is <br />\n<br />\n但唔係好熟 同埋大家都明要寫落手先知好唔好用 所以想問下大家呢兩隻既好壞處 比起codeigniter又有咩好咩唔好咁 language上同javascript/jquery 既syntax係咪差唔多?<br />\n<br />\n小弟聽日考試 可能會遲少少覆 大家可以拋下磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aabc72af981f3c17a8b78b96558f9952a7f90c3","tid":22864,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:21:07.000Z","msg":"angularjs同nodejs 一個frontend一個backend<br />\n本身都冇衝突, 我唔明你要諗啲乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\njquery只係一個library, 本質上都係js, 所以冇所謂嘅syntax<br />\n<br />\nphp比較古老, 唔會點變, 即係唔洗點追新嘢<br />\njs潛力就大好多, frontend/backend都用得<br />\n其實已經可以寫埋desktop application, 直接存取file system, hardware<br />\n不過就學撚死你, 喺我打緊呢篇回覆嘅時候可能已經又有新library/framwork出咗<br />\n<br />\n寫得web嘅話就算你用php都好難避免唔用js<br />\n所以集中寫js會著數好多"},{"pid":"22ccbd4f31ec4bdfb1cf58fcd77094b1733eb2c1","tid":22864,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"如果你打算用angularjs+nodejs<br />\n我建議你直接用meanjs<br />\n會慳返好多時間"},{"pid":"38c10d408cc35a44ac7e293729ccf4adf4f5f91b","tid":22864,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:26:22.000Z","msg":"之前FYP 用過codeigniter 寫落都幾簡單<br />\n<br />\n但係出嚟做野見到D J2EE或者js framework 就覺得自己好似乜撚都唔識咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我條Team個application用spring framework 寫，d developer 係印度，我地香港淨係做deployment同production support，咩都學唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最撚令人氣餒既係當我地揾到有Bug 報比佢地，佢地話係spring framework 既問題唔關佢地事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準備拎埋bonus走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a966c762f624a0af46c96a06ebff3192970b9ba3","tid":22864,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你打算用angularjs+nodejs<br />\n我建議你直接用meanjs<br />\n會慳返好多時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等我search下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f262cf7bd914dddf427bbacfa9aea91d9b254853","tid":22864,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T17:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>angularjs同nodejs 一個frontend一個backend<br />\n本身都冇衝突, 我唔明你要諗啲乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\njquery只係一個library, 本質上都係js, 所以冇所謂嘅syntax<br />\n<br />\nphp比較古老, 唔會點變, 即係唔洗點追新嘢<br />\njs潛力就大好多, frontend/backend都用得<br />\n其實已經可以寫埋desktop application, 直接存取file system, hardware<br />\n不過就學撚死你, 喺我打緊呢篇回覆嘅時候可能已經又有新library/framwork出咗<br />\n<br />\n寫得web嘅話就算你用php都好難避免唔用js<br />\n所以集中寫js會著數好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係冇做research 純粹問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係既 用js寫可能仲好 係因為第一隻上手係codeigniter 所以用開php"},{"pid":"bc270001ceab6243402963af0f8eb3845cc12f52","tid":22864,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2